func (s *SchedulerImpl) GetAllTasks() []*types.AgentTask {
    // Creates deep copies of every task, every call
    taskCopy := *task
    if len(task.Dependencies) > 0 {
        taskCopy.Dependencies = make([]string, len(task.Dependencies))
        copy(taskCopy.Dependencies, task.Dependencies)
    }
    // ... more deep copies for Metadata, Input
}
```

**Issue**: Expensive deep copy on every call, even if most callers just need status.

**Fix**: Add a `GetTaskIDs()` or `GetTaskStatuses()` method that returns only what's needed. Deep copy only when full task data is required.

